se.cbb.jprime.prm

Class DependenciesCache<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.cbb.jprime.prm.DependenciesCache<T>

  • public class DependenciesCache<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Stores data for a set of Dependencies. In particular, it enables caching of data for invariant dependencies, so that given a new Structure one needs only update values for non-encountered dependencies and those which feature latent variables.

    Only for use when storage requirements (i.e. number of encountered dependencies) are feasible.
